title: New donors flock to Clinton after Benghazi hearing
text: Democratic presidential contender Hillary Rodham Clinton now has a donor base of more than 500,000 supporters, thanks in part to a rush of new contributors who gave money after her 11-hour congressional testimony about the Benghazi attacks Thursday.
